title: UFYB 105: Listener Q&A Vol. 15
itunes:title: Listener Q&A Vol. 15
description:
The topics I’m covering range from general questions on classic thought work issues to some more specific questions from life coaches that I think will be super helpful to all of you. From the importance of niches, the belief that external factors could make you happy, to letting go of your emotional childhood, I’ve got it all covered today.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://unfuckyourbrain.com/105
